<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-in-the-habit-of-have-a-the-habit-of">be in the habit of / have a / the habit of</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>有…的习惯：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He's in the habit of getting up late on the weekend.
他有周末晚起的习惯。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you have the habit of offering your seat to the old on the bus?
乘车时你有主动给老人让座的习惯吗？</p></div></div>